{"tid":1730302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想求poly手足就入黎推","createTime":"2019-11-17T13:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T13:26:24.000Z","uid":201662,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1866a2dad98060b501dcf4b3070caa2446111b90","tid":1730302,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"只有2條路你地自己揀，但都有個特點就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要人前後夾擊班狗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論最後係向邊一邊走，poly手足都唔好主動出擊，等到有一邊係夠人做前後夾擊時先攻出去，咁先有機會走到，係走之前請帶好裝備，係徹退時使用，以拖延佢地行軍速度，同時依家要開始set rb，係徹退時就一無顧慮咁跑<br />\n<br />\n希望有家長車可以準備接仔女，因為今次係香港嘅dunkirk，走得幾多就幾多，只要有人走甩就係我地勝利<br />\n<br />\n軍事上大勝易，險敗難，點樣唔大敗先係最難嘅課題，只要留得青山在，那怕冇柴燒<br />\n<br />\n香港人，合作"},{"pid":"f7baad2d5db9928f3bcd556540472bbdb6813efb","tid":1730302,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31ff5e9125bb401209393f63f6a5d72dc91e0aa5","tid":1730302,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:09:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理大已經完全被包圍，入面既手足係無得走呀！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">遍地開花根本救唔到理大，要救只能夠去理大附近打出一個缺口！！</span><br />\n唔好再吹遍地開花喇！！理大精銳勇武完全被圍捕，唔救就無幾百個勇武架喇！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a6cb7b9cd4e0b0969a94248a7ab5f4c3aa57511f","tid":1730302,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"419cb72003b05f84a7675c92d05b7cd67d6f9b16","tid":1730302,"uid":198981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:09:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28b88a80593336da6bb0f4a1b078c151a03ac8e7","tid":1730302,"uid":173137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh"},{"pid":"030412b29dfaec703bdfb31da03255cb2469fadb","tid":1730302,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"poly 全場共識 死守<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1730253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1730253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n死守嘅結果好大可能會失去所有手足，輕則10年，重則被自殺<br />\n<br />\n要去求佢地啊"},{"pid":"2c12019899a93a110860d4bf2291f2d0ebf4e23c","tid":1730302,"uid":189443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"dca3a969791ba719dcb18acf83f6394daf5214c5","tid":1730302,"uid":94137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be9fbf74d98540518391219062ac69893b92f31","tid":1730302,"uid":129594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95d73681b4de7f466e2615a9d7d85da2b718a0a2","tid":1730302,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63ace14dbdbac7664a9a47b99f6d2d2b981ae3cb","tid":1730302,"uid":272275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56895c8f3a5b9f92fa709f9e483333afff86595a","tid":1730302,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"十八區開花"},{"pid":"a8666b0cd855033f0f6b9ee12dcc477163524b3c","tid":1730302,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"唔好死"},{"pid":"fb069e97196b160b390618e77fca000876b27470","tid":1730302,"uid":54965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:1